      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 53 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 53 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>漸，女歸吉，利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Jian suggests to us the marriage of a young lady, and the good fortune (attending it). There will be advantage in being firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
