      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 53 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 53 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：鴻漸于干，小子厲，有言，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows the wild geese gradually approaching the shore. A young officer (in similar circumstances) will be in a position of danger, and be spoken against; but there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
