      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 53 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：鴻漸于木，或得其桷，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows the geese gradually advanced to the trees. They may light on the flat branches. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
