      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 53 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：鴻漸于逵，其羽可用為儀，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth NINE, undivided, shows the geese gradually advanced to the large heights (beyond). Their feathers can be used as ornaments. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
